Description: A package for creating Next-Generation Clustered Heat Maps
    (NG-CHMs). NG-CHMs allow for dynamic exploration of heat map data in a
    web browser. 'NGCHM' allows users to create stand-alone HTML files
    containing a Next-Generation Clustered Heat Map and/or .ngchm files to
    view in the NG-CHM viewer.
